### 1. Luo uusi käyttäjä
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "username": "JohnDoe",
  "email": "kalle@metropolia.fi",
  "password": "salainen-salasana"
}

### 2. Kirjaudu sisään
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "JohnDoe",
  "password": "salainen-salasana"
}

@token = <paste-token-here>

### 3. Hae oma profiili tokenilla
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Paivita oma kayttaja (vaihda id omaan user_id:hen)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/39
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated"
}

### 5. Yrita paivittaa toisen kissa (pitaisi palauttaa 403, jos et ole owner/admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats/41
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "cat_name": "Not allowed",
  "weight": 3.2
}

### 6. Error handler testi: tyhja user body (pitaisi palauttaa JSON error 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 7. Luo kissa multipartina (kentan nimi on file)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cat_name"

TestiKissa
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="weight"

3.4
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="birthdate"

2020-01-01
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cat.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./public/cat.jpg
--WebAppBoundary--

### 8. Error handler testi: virheellinen tiedostotyyppi (pitaisi palauttaa JSON error 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cat_name"

BadFileCat
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="weight"

3.1
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="birthdate"

2020-01-01
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="note.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./README.md
--WebAppBoundary--

